      <title>卢拉访问玻利维亚寻求政变失败后左翼势力的统一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lula-visits-bolivia-seeking-to-unify-the-left-after-failed-coup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西的路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦正在努力统一玻利维亚分裂的社会主义运动，这是一项艰巨的任务，即使对总统路易斯·阿尔塞发动政变失败也无法实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lula-visits-bolivia-seeking-to-unify-the-left-after-failed-coup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示法国勒庞将赢得首轮总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-le-pen-would-win-first-round-president-vote-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投票结束后进行的一项民意调查显示，尽管玛丽娜·勒庞所领导的极右翼政党国民联盟在周日的立法选举中跌至第三位，但她将在 2027 年法国下一届总统选举的第一轮选举中领先。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-le-pen-would-win-first-round-president-vote-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:47:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪在政治僵局中对法国债务前景发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/moody-s-warns-on-french-debt-outlook-amid-political-gridlock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪投资者服务公司表示，如果政治争论导致法国的财政和债务指标大幅恶化，法国的主权评级将面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/moody-s-warns-on-french-debt-outlook-amid-political-gridlock</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:37:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总统候选人玛丽娜·勒庞面临 2022 年竞选资金调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-le-pen-faces-probe-into-possible-illegal-campaign-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴黎检察官称，极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞因涉嫌在 2022 年总统竞选失败期间提供非法竞选资金而面临法国调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-le-pen-faces-probe-into-possible-illegal-campaign-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:37:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
