    <item>
      <title>投票前对冲基金押注英镑走强创六年来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/hedge-funds-piled-into-bets-for-stronger-pound-before-uk-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周英国大选前，对冲基金对英镑走强的押注飙升至六年多来的最高水平，因为投资者相信工党的胜利将给该国的政治和经济带来稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/hedge-funds-piled-into-bets-for-stronger-pound-before-uk-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>税收改革计划出台前，英国非本土人口增长 7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/britain-s-non-dom-population-rose-7-ahead-of-tax-revamp-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在各大政党最近提出废除税收优惠制度的提议之前，申请享受海外收入和收益税收优惠的英国富裕居民数量上升了约 7.4%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/britain-s-non-dom-population-rose-7-ahead-of-tax-revamp-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:29:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普重返迈阿密竞选活动 拜登力挫反抗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/trump-taps-miami-for-return-to-trail-as-biden-fights-off-revolt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在对手乔·拜登总统陷入激烈竞争之际，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 低调数日，如今重新出现在竞选活动中。而拜登则顶住了党内要求其让位给更年轻的民主党候选人的呼声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/trump-taps-miami-for-return-to-trail-as-biden-fights-off-revolt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利开始对布达佩斯市长选举进行全面重新计票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/hungary-starts-full-recount-in-knife-edge-budapest-mayoral-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个月前，自由派现任市长以微弱优势击败了总理维克托·奥尔班领导的执政党支持的候选人，匈牙利开始对布达佩斯市长选举进行全面重新计票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/hungary-starts-full-recount-in-knife-edge-budapest-mayoral-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 08:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
